data.description: This Spacious 3 Bedroom, 3 Bathroom home has many updates throughout! New flooring, Carpet, Lighting fixtures, Electrical upgrades, New Doors, New Deck, New Appliances, and New Paint. Very large Family room with wood burning stove! Relax in your sunroom that overlooks your fenced in back yard with a cool tree house/deck!  Partially finished basement for extra entertaining and plenty of storage space.   Appliances included and Move in Ready! Call today for your private showing!
